### Summary Stack

- **Vue 3** + Composition API + TypeScript
- **CSS Variables** — No Tailwind, BEM naming (- only)
- **CSS Properties** — Not Allowed em, rem
- **Container Properties** — vw unit or 100%
- **Robust Responsive Design** — Mobile-first approach

